metadata.title: IMS Database from Alaska

creators.name: University of Alaska Fairbanks (UAF), School of Fisheries
Ocean Sciences (SFOS), Institute of Marine Science (IMS)

metadata.description: IMS Database contains oceanographic data from sea and oceans surrounding Alaska; data holdings include CTD, current meter/ tide gauge, nutrient chemistry, primary productivity, zooplankton, benthic organisms and sediment data.
metadata.notes:
Purpose: To support oceanographic research.

Status: In Progress
